A lot of the scaffolding here is lifted from that project: the state
model, job tracking, command layout, skills, and most of the test
harness. The CLI adapter in scripts/lib/qwen.mjs is rewritten from
scratch to speak Qwen Code's stream-json format instead of the Codex
app-server JSON-RPC protocol, since Qwen has no persistent server
subcommand.
